title: The Audible: How Alabama can prove it's not a fraud vs. Texas A
text:
Updated Oct 15, 2015 at 10:33a ET 
On a new episode of The Audible, Bruce Feldman and Stewart Mandel look ahead to the Alabama-Texas A&M game and discuss how much is on the line for both teams. 
It's a huge test for the Aggies ' defense, while the Crimson Tide need to prove they're not a playoff fraud by handling Kyle Allen and A&M's explosive offense. 
Click on the embedded player above to listen to the clip. You can also get every episode of The Audible delivered to you by subscribing on iTunes .
